## About
This source code come from [Ola H채rkeg책rd](http://research.harkegard.se/). and the default readme is `/QCAT/README`, the doc of lib is [here](http://research.harkegard.se/qcat/index.html) or `/QCAT/doc/`, the code is in `/QCAT/qcat/`. Thanks to [Ola H채rkeg책rd](http://research.harkegard.se/) for his excellent work in getting us such a powerful library.

## Test 
We used this project as a library in the [control_allocation project](https://github.com/mengchaoheng/control_allocation) and wrote several test files to learn the use of this library. Run the `test_qcatxxx` of the [control_allocation project](https://github.com/mengchaoheng/control_allocation) to view the usage.
